> Regarding Scheduler/AM HA, I have hit an open issue in REEF. This feature might need to wait a bit.
> Can you please elaborate this?

@kramasamy - REEF supports AM HA on .Net/Windows only. Java implementation is work in progress (REEF-345). In absence of this feature if REEF driver crashes, topology scheduler here, YARN will shut down all the containers allocated to the topology.

@saileshmittal Okay, that makes sense, but I think that two things need to happen here:
1. The previous Heron UI runbook doc that I linked to needs to have any redundant material removed to make way for this doc
2. This new doc needs to contain links to the runbook doc
